HEADWORD: Earnestness
<hw>Ear"nest*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
earnest; intentness; anxiety.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An honest <qex>earnestness</qex> in the young man's manner.</q>
<rj><qau>W. Irving.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Earnful</ent>⟦br⟧
